              ],
              "free_text": [
                " Differential range telescope with 4",
                " scintillation counters and copper absorbers used to",
                " detect scattered protons. Neutron flux monitored with",
                " two telescopes looking at a polyethylene scatterer,",
                " each using two scintillation counters separated by",
                " copper absorbers."
              ]
            },
